::KitKat::

She went up to Megatron.
"ah, sir, I have brought back a friend of Quickstrike's. His name is 
Rowdy. I was wondering if maybe, we, ah, could go out and look for 
Quickstrike."

She felt stupid. She never showed cowardess to anyone. Not untill she 
met Megatron.  She still wanted to repay him for shocking her the day 
they met.  She felt stupid for showing cowardess in front of the 
others and particularly the new wolf in the pack.
